          <b>English:</b>
        </p>

        <p>
          <b>EcoInk</b> is an <b>e-commerce project</b> developed as part of the SAE S5.A.01 course in the 3rd year of a Bachelor's Degree in Computer Science.
        </p>

        <p>
          This web application enables the management and sale of <b>printer cartridges</b>.
        </p>

        <p>
          The project is structured around two main components: a <b>backend</b> developed with <b>NestJS</b> and <b>MongoDB</b>, and a <b>frontend</b> built with <b>Vue.js</b>.
